			Aufderheide, Tim Felix 2020, Early Vedic – Introduction, Part 2: Texts and Transmission. In Saverio Dalpedri, Götz Keydana, and Stavros Skopeteas (eds.), <i>Glottothèque: Ancient Indo-European Grammars online</i> (electronic resource). Göttingen: University of Göttingen. DOI: https://doi.org/10.5446/49491.
			</small></p>
		</div>
    </div>

